www.draconictribe.com <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utygrav.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tygrav</A> at: 5/28/01 3:46:21 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www,kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/28/01 7:03:37 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://dynamic.gamespy.com/~cazic/cazic/ubb/uploads/grimtoo.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: dream world</span><hr size=1> The problem here is my vision of an EPIC weapon is different from Verant's.  First off I'd want it to be an artifact (one perserver of each) and the quest to be different on each server.  Then I'd make the thing rediculously powerful, I would want it to be like Stormbringer for the Shadowknights, something that made you the ultimate in your class and awesome in every way.<br>
<br>
So yeah, a 400 point Lure.  Gee, that's powerful... isn't that the POINT? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uariachne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ariachne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/1/01 10:54:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: compare Wizards to other casters </span><hr size=1> Bow to the other mage.<br>
<br>
I am a 52 mage that regularly, consistantly,always groups with a 51 Wiz, who always outdamages me and my pet in a fight.  As it should be.  By the time I have the pet where it should beget it on the right mob and start hitting malo on the bad guy so the wiz can hit full as much as possible, I am not contibuting that much to the fight in nukes.  So over a short figh, the wiz wins.<br>
<br>
Now you did say over time didn't you, well any fight you have that is going to be &quot;over time&quot; my pet will hit, but I will be resisted.  Mage resist is alot higher, I get to dmg shield, summon and malo the bad guy, when malo sticks, I get to nuke.  Wiz still beats me.  Right on with me, not a complaint, just an observation.  I have grouped with this wiz A LONG time, I was there for his frustrations in the 30's when I could outdamage him, but, nothing makes me happier now then to see him outdamage me, it is just a might ridiculous you have to wait for 44 to see that happen.<br>
